quran[5{c,v,t}:
33,31,aur tum mein se jo Allah aur uss ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki itaat kere gi aur naik amal kere gi is ko hum dohra ajar den ge aur hum ne is ke liye rizaq kareem muhayya kar rakha hai
33,32,"NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki byoyo, tum aam aurton ki terhan nahi ho agar tum Allah se darny wali ho to dubi zabaan se baat nah kya karo ke dil ki kharabi ka mubtala koi shakhs lalach mein par jaye, balkay saaf seedhi baat karo"
33,33,"apne gharon mein tِk kar raho aur sabiq daur jahliat ki si sajh dhaj nah dukhati phiro namaz qaim karo, zkoh do aur Allah aur uss ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki itaat karo Allah to yeh chahta hai ke ehley beeet NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam se gandagi ko daur kere aur tumhe poori terhan pak kar day"
33,34,yaad rakho Allah ki ayaat aur hikmat ki baton ko jo tumahray gharon mein sunai jati hain be shak Allah lateef aur bakhabar hai
33,35,"bilyaqeen jo mard aur jo aurtain muslim hain, momin hain, Mutee farmaan hain, raast baz hain, sabir hain, Allah ke agay jhuknay walay hain, sadqa dainay walay hain, roza rakhnay walay hain, apni sharamgahon ki hifazat karne walay hain, aur Allah ko kasrat se yaad karne walay hain, Allah ne un ke liye mughfirat aur bara ajar muhayya kar rakha hai"
